{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But instead of going around and looking for labor, they used to come up to the committee and say, today we need 200 people to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the same week, they came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said all the men should come out in the middle-- in the middle of the city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they picked up the strongest 200 people, including one of my uncle, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what city were you in and this point?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All in Miedzyrzecz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said they going to take them to Kiev to work, to slave there in the field, in the forest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a lie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took them out only not even 5 miles in the same grave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They digged a small grave where tried another the 3,000 people, these 200.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they didn't want these strong people in case they're going to fight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they did it mostly in these small towns that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took out the cream, the strong men, right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they could fight, I mean, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- after that, Ukrainian people told us quietly they were killed there, all kind, slice up with knives, whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they made them digging the grave, and they buried them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the first week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when was-- do you remember what year this was?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Probably, it was February the 14th.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it probably would be February the 8th?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The 26th?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or the 25th?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't say exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No, of course, we lost my aunt, my uncle, and one of my cousin, the strong guy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The woman up till day, she was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'll-- I'll say later on about the woman what happened by the grave.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
